definition: short note/slip of paper/stripe/(slang) cop/(old) prostitute
strip/item/article/clause (of law or treaty)/classifier for long thin things (ribbon, river, road, trousers etc)

son/child/seed/egg/small thing/1st earthly branch: 11 p.m.-1 a.m., midnight, 11th solar month (7th December to 5th January), year of the Rat/Viscount, fourth of five orders of nobility 五等爵位[wu3 deng3 jue2 wei4]/ancient Chinese compass point: 0° (north)

sentences.english: It is a paper that those gentlemen left for these ladies.
sentences.chinese: 这是那几位先生留给太太们的一张条子。

sentences.english: Thus, cop called his two friends, Mike and John, to identify George.
sentences.chinese: 因此条子叫他的两个朋友过来认尸。

sentences.english: Thin card sliver due to web falling at cards.
sentences.chinese: 由于梳棉棉网下坠导致条子过细。

sentences.english: Pull a brief informal note to be his paste the enlightenment that find a person, before long somebody claim ladle.
sentences.chinese: 拉条子为他张贴了寻人启示，不久有人认领了勺子。

sentences.english: Please stick a piece of paper saying NO TOUCH on the glass counter.
sentences.chinese: 请在玻璃柜上贴一张“请勿触摸”的条子。

sentences.english: Mr Smith pencilled a note and left it on the table.
sentences.chinese: 史密斯先生用铅笔写了张条子留在桌子。

sentences.english: A little crayon drawing, with annoying transparent strips on it.
sentences.chinese: 蜡笔画，有些透明的条子在上面，比较讨厌。

sentences.english: He asked me to pass the note along.
But he never wrote notes like this.
sentences.chinese: 但他从未写过象这样的条子。

sentences.english: You get one too many blue slips and you would be out of Moeller, period.
sentences.chinese: 如果你得的蓝条子多了，那么你将会被踢出学校。

sentences.english: Jack got caught slipping a note to Lisa during the exam.
sentences.chinese: 在考试过程中杰克向莉萨递条子时被发现了。

sentences.english: Like, Choosing sticks, reading tea leaves, palms, or stars;
sentences.chinese: 好比要选木条子，看茶叶，读掌心，观星相等。

sentences.english: He killed 16 people before he was shot dead by police.
sentences.chinese: 他狙死了16人，然后被条子狙了。

sentences.english: Stretch in draw frame sliver fed to roving.
sentences.chinese: 喂入粗纱的条子意外伸长。

sentences.english: Defective operation of sliver feed mechanism.
sentences.chinese: 条子喂入机构运行有故障。
